crontab entry
something to add to crontab to get gardenhose script to restart hourly (blocks sometimes)
( for me this runs on my nano itx always-on server )

start.sh
the script to kick off hourly, streams to a file
( for me this runs on my nano itx always-on server )

fetch_and_chop_last_line.sh
a script to run from my dev box to pull down from my nano itx the most recent tweets

*rb
various little scripts for parsing tweets
